      • reorganize

        public void reorganize(boolean debug)
        When the construction of the graph is finished, it should be "reorganized":
        It is checked, if the vertices which an edge claims to connect exist. If they do not exist, the edges are deleted.
        It is checked, which neighbour vertices a vertex has. Then it is associated directly to them.

      • calculateShortestPaths

        public Path[][] calculateShortestPaths()
        Calculates "All-Pairs Shortest Path" after Floyd-Warshall Algorithm.
        O(n^3), but very handy
        Returns:
        returns a matrix with all pairs of shortest paths

      • getPathMatrix
